    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-commodity\">supremely powerful</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Exosuit Toxin Filtering System</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Drastically improves survival times in <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">toxic environments</span>.",
