    "TencentChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">套装毒性过滤系统</span>的<span class=\"name name-commodity\">至强</span>提升。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>开始安装升级。<br><br>极大地提升<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">毒性环境</span>中的生存时间。",
